        dc:description           "Figure 10. Platypalpus obscurus (von Roser), male terminalia A dorsal view of apex of right epandrial lamella and left cercus B lateral view of apex of right epandrial lamella C epandrium, dorsal D epandrium, left lateral. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 9. Platypalpus obscuroides sp. nov., male terminalia A epandrium, from right side B apex of right epandrial lamella C epandrium and cerci, dorsolateral view D cerci, dorsal view. Abbr. lc: left cercus; lel: left epandrial lamella; ph: phallus; rc: right cercus; rs: right surstylus. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
